(# Acme Customer Support Knowledge Base) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Refund Policy) Tj
T*
(- Customers can request a full refund within 14 days of purchase.) Tj
T*
(- Refund requests after 14 days are evaluated case by case.) Tj
T*
(- Digital subscription renewals are non-refundable once the billing cycle starts.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Cancellation Policy) Tj
T*
(- Monthly plans can be canceled anytime from the account settings page.) Tj
T*
(- Cancellation is effective at the end of the current billing cycle.) Tj
T*
(- Annual plans can be canceled, but remaining months are not prorated.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Shipping and Delivery) Tj
T*
(- Standard shipping ETA is 5 to 7 business days.) Tj
T*
(- Expedited shipping ETA is 1 to 2 business days.) Tj
T*
(- If a package is marked delivered but not received, customers should wait 24 hours before) Tj
T*
(filing a lost package claim.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Account Access Issues) Tj
T*
(- For failed login attempts, customers should reset their password using the forgot-password) Tj
T*
(flow.) Tj
T*
(- Accounts are temporarily locked for 15 minutes after 5 failed attempts.) Tj
T*
(- If 2FA code delivery fails, users should verify phone network availability and retry after 2) Tj
T*
(minutes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Troubleshooting App Errors) Tj
T*
(- Users should clear cache and restart the app for session-related issues.) Tj
T*
(- Persistent crash issues should be escalated with device model, OS version, and timestamp.) Tj
T*
(- Payment-processing errors should be escalated when retrying after 10 minutes still fails.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Escalation Rules) Tj
T*
(- Escalate to human support when the user explicitly asks for a human agent.) Tj
T*
(- Escalate when policy interpretation is ambiguous or legal-risk related.) Tj
T*
(- Escalate when technical issues persist after standard troubleshooting.) Tj
T*
